        <li>
          June 2024: Concluded my research at the HPDIC Lab after presenting my
          work at the UW CS Research Symposium.
        </li>
        <li>
          May 2024: Promoted to Jr. SDE III at Amazon after performance review.
        </li>
        <li>
          January 2024: Joined the HPDIC Lab as an undergraduate researcher
          working on vector databases.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
